The paper deals with planning legged locomotion in complex environments, which is a problem in robotics. Therefore, cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also discusses the use of optimization techniques, which suggests that it could belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision) or cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also deals with ensuring the existence of a quasi-static COM trajectory, which suggests that it could belong to cs.SY (Systems and Control) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
